      <abstract>Member of Co. I, 339th U.S. Infantry who served in the Allied intervention in Russia, 1918-1920, the "Polar Bear Expedition." Collection includes newspaper clippings concerning the return of the 339th to Detroit, Michigan; pictures taken in Archangel; Thanksgiving menu and field order and miscellanea concerning activities of the Polar Bear expedition.</abstract>
      <unitid countrycode="us" repositorycode="MiU-H" encodinganalog="099" type="call number">86608 Aa 1</unitid>
      <langmaterial>The materials are in <language encodinganalog="041" langcode="eng">English.</language></langmaterial>
